	<hr class="line">
	<br>
		Knowledge is power. This is particularly true when it comes to MMOGs where there are literally thousands of quests, weapons, armors, creatures or zones to explore. Our relational database is designed to provides you with comprehensive information that gives you an edge in your favorites games with features like :<br><br>
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="100%">
			<tr style="padding-left:10px;">
				<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-top:8px;"><img src="/images/v6/localized/picto/puce.png" width="5" height="5"></td>
				<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;">Basic and Advanced Items Search</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Search trough the most accurate game database on the net using the basic or the advanced search form. While the basic search offers a quick and easy way to query our database, the advanced search features a full set of powerful filters that allow you to refine your query with great accuracy. Finally you will be able to find the perfect replacement for that rusty old sword you seem to be hooked on!</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-top:8px;"><img src="/images/v6/localized/picto/puce.png" width="5" height="5"></td>
				<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;">Sharing experiences (coming soon)</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Magelo provides a fantastic sharing ground for players by allowing them read and post personal comments such as the best way to get an item, to resolve a quest, or even to beat that nasty creature. Save yourself some time and headache, learn through other's experiences or share your own to the community.</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
