	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:5px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px; padding-left: 45px;">Characters Profiles</div>	
	<div style="position: relative; top: 6px; left:10px;">
		<img class="png32" style="position: absolute; top:0px; left:0px;" src="/images/v6/shared/right_menu/support_icone_off.png" width="33" height="15">
		<img class="png32" style="position: absolute;top:-15px; left:4px;" src="/images/v6/shared/right_menu/premium_icone.png" width="24" height="24">
	</div>
	<hr class="line">
	<br>
		A character profile is a way to create a <b>persistence of your character out of the game</b>, offline so to speak. Character profiles appeared for the first time back in 2001 when Magelo published the first profiling system on the web. Since then, it has grown up in popularity and became an essential tool for most MMOGs players.<br><br>A character profile is an excellent tool to <b>help you define your character's development strategy</b>. Because now your character sheet is available out of the game, you can quietly review its skills, attributes, talents, etc., compares them with others profiles and assess your strength and weakness.<br><br>Also, by <b>linking your profile on your forum signature</b>, you can show to your community what your character is made off, what are your achievements, your build, your current equipment as well as your alternatives ones. It's a unique way to show the result of your hard work!<br><br>Guilds too are making a good use of Magelo Profiles. Many rely on them and the Magelo Roster to gauge the overall might of their guild and to help them plan their strategic roadmap.<br><br>Guilds also use Magelo Profiles during their recruitment process. Because profiles can be authenticated trough the Premium offer, guilds are assured that they are genuine. Magelo is the only system that provides such guarantee for <b>guilds willing to maximize their recruitment</b>.<br><br>
		<table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="2" width="100%">
			<tr style="padding-left:10px;">
				<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-top:8px;"><img src="/images/v6/localized/picto/puce.png" width="5" height="5"></td>
				<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;">Magelo Update</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td><a href="magelo_update.jspa">Magelo Update</a>&nbsp;(MU) is our game data collector as well as our profiles synchronization program. You will need to run it to get the most of our Premium features. Based on Java Web Start technology, <b>MU is lightweight, reliable and easy to use</b>. Until now more than 100'000 users decided to put their trust on it. No use of third-party languages, multiple add-ons, manual updates and so on. Just launch MU, and you are good to go!</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-top:8px;"><img src="/images/v6/localized/picto/puce.png" width="5" height="5"></td>
				<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;">Profiles synchronization</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>With Magelo Update (MU), <b>creating and updating a Magelo Profile is really easy</b>. Once MU is launched, start your game session as usual. All your character's data will be collected and sent over Magelo to create and update your profile.<br>The amount of data transmitted is small enough to not alter your game performance.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-top:8px;"><img src="/images/v6/localized/picto/puce.png" width="5" height="5"></td>
				<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;">Profiles authentication</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Every time you synchronize your profile, an "<b>Authentic Profile" stamp</b> will be applied on it. <br>This stamp will <b>guarantee that your profile is indeed genuine and unaltered</b>. Only Magelo can bring you such guarantee and protect you from fake and inaccurate profiles that some are offering.</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-top:8px;"><img src="/images/v6/localized/picto/puce.png" width="5" height="5"></td>
				<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;">Profiles customization</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Start customizing your profile by selecting one of the backgrounds available or by creating one yourself. There are also many awesome artists out there wich are providing their services to the community. Check them out! <br>And if you want to push the fun even further, you can link music to your profile too!</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td style="vertical-align:top; padding-top:8px;"><img src="/images/v6/localized/picto/puce.png" width="5" height="5"></td>
				<td style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 13px;">Signatures (coming soon)</td>
			</tr>
			<tr>
				<td>&nbsp;</td>
				<td>Signatures are an important part of a profile. It's the best way to link it in your favorite forum or communication tool. <br>Build your dynamic signature to your liking with our <b>Sig Maker</b> : You can display <b>dynamic data</b> (level, AA, HP, MANA, tradeskills...) wherever you want on a custom background and <b>skin it as you wish</b> (font color/size/family). You will never have to worry about updating your signatures data ever again, Magelo will do it for you.</td>
			</tr>
		</table>
